OL,3,CCouple 'devastated' at repeated
OL,4,Cmaternity failings more than 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FWatch Nancy Cole's exclusive report as
OL,8,Fa couple who lost their baby in
OL,9,Fhospital more than 30 years ago, share
OL,10,Ftheir pain over maternity care
OL,11,Ffailings that are still happening now.
OL,13,FA couple whose baby daughter died over
OL,14,F30 years ago at the Nottingham
OL,15,Fhospital trust under investigation for
OL,16,Fits maternity care said they are
OL,17,Fdevastated to see the failings when
OL,18,Fshe died, are still happening now.
