OL,5,Con
OL,7,FMarie and Brian Kelly's daughter Laura
OL,8,Fwas born at Queens Medical Centre in
OL,9,FNottingham on the 23rd November 1991.
OL,11,FMarie, who at the time was a 21-year-
OL,12,Fold first time mum, recalls being
OL,13,Fignored by staff despite being in
OL,14,F"agony" because her "waters had gone."
OL,16,F"The midwife said I'd just wet the
OL,17,Fbed," Marie said, "Another lady came
OL,18,Falong, an auxiliary, she knew it was
OL,19,Fmy waters but she couldn't go above
OL,20,Fthe midwife."
