OL,3,CCouple 'devastated' at repeated
OL,4,Cmaternity failings more than 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FEventually, she said: "The midwife
OL,8,Fcame in with a wheelchair but I
OL,9,Fcouldn't sit down.
OL,11,F"Obviously it was Laura's head but I
OL,12,Fdidn't know that. I was saying I
OL,13,Fcouldn't sit down and she was just
OL,14,Framming me through doors and down
OL,15,Fcorridors, saying "you sit down.
OL,17,F"But I couldn't sit down because there
OL,18,Fwas something there and obviously it
OL,19,Fwas, Laura was ready to be born."
OL,26,@oD@WOUwD@SOU{D@aO]
