OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F371A1738851921
OL,3,CCouple 'devastated' at repeated
OL,4,Cmaternity failings more than 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FLaura was rushed to the neonatal unit
OL,8,Fat City Hospital in Nottingham because
OL,9,Fshe had difficulty breathing. She died
OL,10,Fthe day after she was born.
OL,12,F"A doctor came up, sat on my bed and
OL,13,Fheld my hand and said there have been
OL,14,Fmassive mistakes made and we will be
OL,15,Flooking into it. " Marie said.
OL,17,F"They knew what they had done. If
OL,18,FLaura had been born when she was ready
OL,19,Fto be born she'd be here today, that's
OL,20,Fthe sad thing about it."
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@ROUyD@AOU|D@XO]
