OL,4,Cmaternity failings more than 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FLast year, the couple met with many of
OL,8,Fthe families involved in the
OL,9,FNottingham Ockenden review.
OL,11,F"It's the same old thing, paperwork
OL,12,Fchanged, paperwork missing"
OL,14,FBrian has been devastated to see so
OL,15,Fmany similarities in failings in his
OL,16,Fwife and daughter's care, to more
OL,17,Frecent experiences.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
