OL,3,CCouple 'devastated' at repeated
OL,4,Cmaternity failings more than 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"Not being looked after, badly
OL,8,Ftreated, no plugs on monitors in
OL,9,Frooms, nothing has changed." Brian
OL,10,Fsaid before adding: "It's the same old
OL,11,Fthing. Paperwork changed, paperwork
OL,12,Fmissing, notes rubbed out."
OL,14,FTo add to the family's trauma, ten
OL,15,Fyears after Laura died the couple were
OL,16,Ftold, despite not agreeing to it, that
OL,17,FLaura's organs had been taken without
OL,18,Fconsent.
