OL,5,Con
OL,7,FIn 2000, 40 families were contacted by
OL,8,FNottingham University Hospitals Trust
OL,9,Fwhere body parts were taken without
OL,10,Fconsent.
OL,12,FMore than a thousand families in
OL,13,FNottinghamshire are thought to have
OL,14,Fbeen affected by what was known as the
OL,15,Forgan scandal, involving hospitals
OL,16,Fnationally.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
