OL,3,CCouple 'devastated' at repeated
OL,4,Cmaternity failings more than 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,FIn a statement Tracy Pilcher, Chief
OL,8,FNurse at NUH said: "I would like to
OL,9,Foffer my sincere apologies to Marie
OL,10,Fand Brian Kelly for the care they and
OL,11,Ftheir daughter, Laura, received in
OL,12,F1991, and for the additional distress
OL,13,Fcaused to them in relation to their
OL,14,Fexperiences following her death.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
