OL,3,CCouple 'devastated' at repeated
OL,4,Cmaternity failings more than 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"We are committed to hearing from and
OL,8,Flistening to those individuals who
OL,9,Fhave concerns about their care in our
OL,10,Fmaternity services, and that includes
OL,11,Fthose whose cases do not fit into the
OL,12,Fscope of the Independent Maternity
OL,13,FReview.
OL,15,F"We will review Laura and Marie's
OL,16,Fcare, and we will update the family
OL,17,Fwith the outcome of that review.
