OL,3,CCouple 'devastated' at repeated
OL,4,Cmaternity failings more than 30 years
OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"We are working hard to improve our
OL,8,Fmaternity services and have a
OL,9,Fmaternity improvement programme that
OL,10,Flooks at every area of the service we
OL,11,Fprovide.
OL,13,F"We know there is more to do, but
OL,14,Flistening to these women will help us
OL,15,Flearn from the past and help us to
OL,16,Ffoster a culture in which staff can
OL,17,Fcontinue that improvement journey."
OL,19,FMarie and Brian are hopeful to finally
OL,20,Fget answers, saying: "We've waited 33
OL,21,Fyears for this."
