OL,5,Con
OL,7,F"Things need to be said." Brian said
OL,8,Fbefore adding: "They've got to start
OL,9,Flooking at the past.
OL,11,F"We've got to open these doors and
OL,12,Ffind out the truth, why is it still
OL,13,Fhappening?"
